  "id": "RAW_430e997a",
  "title": "METR 的 Joel Becker 谈指数级时间跨度评估、威胁模型及 AI 生产力的极限",
  "url": "https://www.latent.space/p/metr",
  "date": "2026-02-27 19:17:52",
  "author": "Latent.Space",
  "siteName": "Latent Space",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div dir=\"auto\" class=\"body markup\">\n   <p><em><a href=\"https://www.ai.engineer/europe\" rel>AIE Europe CFP</a><span> and AIE World’s Fair </span><a href=\"https://www.caisconf.org/pages/cfp/\" rel>paper submissions for CAIS</a><span> peer review are due TODAY - do not delay! Last call ever.</span></em></p>\n   <p>We’re excited to welcome METR for their first LS Pod, hopefully the first of many:</p>\n   <div id=\"youtube2-9QSm_mRGpN8\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;9QSm_mRGpN8&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"Youtube2ToDOM\" class=\"youtube-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"youtube-inner\">\n     <iframe src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/9QSm_mRGpN8?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0\" frameborder=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" gesture=\"media\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowautoplay=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\"></iframe>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p><span>METR are keepers of currently the </span><a href=\"https://x.com/AISafetyMemes/status/2025033374562148433?s=20\" rel>single most infamous chart in AI</a><span>:</span></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_523f6f80-7daf-4e69-a8bd-be64c713ac17_908x1284.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset can-restack\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_523f6f80-7daf-4e69-a8bd-be64c713ac17_908x1284.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_523f6f80-7daf-4e69-a8bd-be64c713ac17_908x1284.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_523f6f80-7daf-4e69-a8bd-be64c713ac17_908x1284.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227193310_523f6f80-7daf-4e69-a8bd-be64c713ac17_908x1284.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_523f6f80-7daf-4e69-a8bd-be64c713ac17_908x1284.png\" width=\"406\" height=\"574.1233480176212\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/523f6f80-7daf-4e69-a8bd-be64c713ac17_908x1284.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1284,&quot;width&quot;:908,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:406,&quot;bytes&quot;:408780,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://www.latent.space/i/189159777?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F523f6f80-7daf-4e69-a8bd-be64c713ac17_908x1284.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227193310_523f6f80-7daf-4e69-a8bd-be64c713ac17_908x1284.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227193310_523f6f80-7daf-4e69-a8bd-be64c713ac17_908x1284.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227193310_523f6f80-7daf-4e69-a8bd-be64c713ac17_908x1284.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_523f6f80-7daf-4e69-a8bd-be64c713ac17_908x1284.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" fetchpriority=\"high\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n           </g>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p>But every Latent Space reader should be sophisticated enough to know that the details matter and that hype and hyperbole go hand in hand in AI social media, because the millions of impressions that got, by people who don’t understand or care about the nuances, disclaimers, and error bars, far outreaches the 69k views on the corrections by the people who actually made the chart:</p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_70ec218d-6d68-416e-b282-876a09f70b05_1572x1702.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset can-restack\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_70ec218d-6d68-416e-b282-876a09f70b05_1572x1702.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227193310_70ec218d-6d68-416e-b282-876a09f70b05_1572x1702.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227193311_70ec218d-6d68-416e-b282-876a09f70b05_1572x1702.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227193310_70ec218d-6d68-416e-b282-876a09f70b05_1572x1702.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_70ec218d-6d68-416e-b282-876a09f70b05_1572x1702.png\" width=\"504\" height=\"545.5384615384615\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/70ec218d-6d68-416e-b282-876a09f70b05_1572x1702.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1576,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:504,&quot;bytes&quot;:810419,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://www.latent.space/i/189159777?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F70ec218d-6d68-416e-b282-876a09f70b05_1572x1702.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_70ec218d-6d68-416e-b282-876a09f70b05_1572x1702.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227193310_70ec218d-6d68-416e-b282-876a09f70b05_1572x1702.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227193310_70ec218d-6d68-416e-b282-876a09f70b05_1572x1702.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_70ec218d-6d68-416e-b282-876a09f70b05_1572x1702.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n           </g>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p><span>There’s a lot of nuance both in making benchmarks (as we discovered </span><a href=\"https://www.latent.space/p/swe-bench-dead\" rel>with OpenAI on our SWE-Bench Verified podcast</a><span>) and in extrapolating results from them, especially </span><a href=\"https://www.swyx.io/scurves\" rel>where exponentials and sigmoids are concerned</a><span>. METR’s Long Horizons work itself has known biases that the authors have responsibly disclosed, but go far too underappreciated in the pursuit of doomer chart porn.</span></p>\n   <a href=\"https://x.com/shashwatgoel7/status/2002369517499105443?s=46\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-component-name=\"Twitter2ToDOM\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset\"> \n    <div data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://x.com/shashwatgoel7/status/2002369517499105443?s=46&quot;,&quot;full_text&quot;:&quot;New Blogpost: How to game the METR plot🚨\\n\\nIn 2025, a single graph changed AGI timelines, investments, research priorities, model quality assessments and much more. \\n\\nBut if you squint harder, only 14 prompts shaped AI discourse over this year. Thats all the data in the 1-4 hour &quot;,&quot;username&quot;:&quot;ShashwatGoel7&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Shashwat Goel&quot;,&quot;profile_image_url&quot;:&quot;https://pbs.substack.com/profile_images/1799099355502419968/F2ztQFj8_normal.jpg&quot;,&quot;date&quot;:&quot;2025-12-20T13:24:29.000Z&quot;,&quot;photos&quot;:[{&quot;img_url&quot;:&quot;https://pbs.substack.com/media/G8nUYUAbMAg5vBB.jpg&quot;,&quot;link_url&quot;:&quot;https://t.co/mxQdDvNXM7&quot;}],&quot;quoted_tweet&quot;:{},&quot;reply_count&quot;:39,&quot;retweet_count&quot;:70,&quot;like_count&quot;:771,&quot;impression_count&quot;:205530,&quot;expanded_url&quot;:null,&quot;video_url&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true}\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-12 pc-padding-16 pc-reset bg-primary-zk6FDl outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-md sizing-border-box-DggLA4 pressable-lg-kV7yq8 font-text-qe4AeH tweet-fWkQfo twitter-embed\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-row pc-gap-12 pc-alignItems-center pc-reset\">\n      <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n       <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" title=\"User\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n        <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_F2ztQFj8.jpg 40w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_F2ztQFj8.jpg 80w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227193310_F2ztQFj8.jpg 120w\" sizes=\"40px\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_F2ztQFj8.jpg\" sizes=\"40px\" alt=\"X avatar for @ShashwatGoel7\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_F2ztQFj8.jpg 40w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_F2ztQFj8.jpg 80w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_F2ztQFj8.jpg 120w\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" draggable=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img-OACg1c object-fit-cover-u4ReeV pencraft pc-reset\"></picture>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-reset flex-grow-rzmknG\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset weight-semibold-uqA4FV reset-IxiVJZ\">Shashwat Goel</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s reset-IxiVJZ\">@ShashwatGoel7</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px;\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke=\"#000\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n       <g>\n        <title></title><path stroke=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M13.2879 19.1666L8.66337 12.575L2.87405 19.1666H0.424805L7.57674 11.0258L0.424805 0.833252H6.71309L11.0717 7.04577L16.5327 0.833252H18.982L12.1619 8.59699L19.5762 19.1666H13.2879ZM16.0154 17.3083H14.3665L3.93176 2.69159H5.58092L9.7601 8.54422L10.4828 9.55981L16.0154 17.3083Z\"></path>\n       </g>\n      </svg>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-15-Psle70 weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ text-aFN1BV\">New Blogpost: How to game the METR plot🚨 In 2025, a single graph changed AGI timelines, investments, research priorities, model quality assessments and much more. But if you squint harder, only 14 prompts shaped AI discourse over this year. Thats all the data in the 1-4 hour</div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset bg-black-dCpgGg outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-sm overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 container-aGHQ9p\">\n      <img src=\"https://pbs.substack.com/media/G8nUYUAbMAg5vBB.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"image-c_FmAR\">\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">1:24 PM · Dec 20, 2025</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">206K Views</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">39 Replies</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">70 Reposts</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">771 Likes</span>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div> \n   </a>\n   <p></p>\n   <p><span>If you’re interested in a short, sharable TED talk version of this pod, over at AIE CODE we were blessed to feature Joel twice, as a </span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RhfqQKe22ZA\" rel>stage talk</a><span> and with a longer form </span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k1t2xyWMUdY&amp;t=850s\" rel>small workshop with Q&amp;A</a><span>:</span></p>\n   <div id=\"youtube2-RhfqQKe22ZA\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;RhfqQKe22ZA&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"Youtube2ToDOM\" class=\"youtube-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"youtube-inner\">\n     <iframe src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/RhfqQKe22ZA?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0\" frameborder=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" gesture=\"media\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowautoplay=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"728\" height=\"409\"></iframe>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p><span>We also make sure cover some of METR’s lesser known work on Threat Evaluation but also Developer Productivity, where 2x friend of the pod and now Zyphra founder </span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-gE1cesJF9M&amp;t=2631s\" rel>Quentin Anthony was the ONLY productive participant</a><span>!</span></p>\n   <p></p>\n   <p><span>Finally, if you’re the sort to read these show notes to the end, then you definitely deserve some pictures of Joel shredding the guitar at </span><a href=\"https://partiful.com/e/v4iE3Num9mRdXnqyLXZS\" rel>Love Band Karaoke</a><span> which we mention at the end: </span></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_261a048d-97ff-4b93-8b13-985257f8faa5_1024x768.jpeg\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset can-restack\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_261a048d-97ff-4b93-8b13-985257f8faa5_1024x768.jpeg 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_261a048d-97ff-4b93-8b13-985257f8faa5_1024x768.jpeg 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_261a048d-97ff-4b93-8b13-985257f8faa5_1024x768.jpeg 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227193310_261a048d-97ff-4b93-8b13-985257f8faa5_1024x768.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227193309_261a048d-97ff-4b93-8b13-985257f8faa5_1024x768.jpeg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" data-attrs=\"{&quot